G = nx.Graph(list(zip(JJ['Source'], JJ['Target'])), weigth = JJ['Frequency'])

options = {
    "font_size": 12,
    "node_size": 10,
    "node_color": "#A0CBE2",
    "edge_color": "skyblue",
    "linewidths": 1,
    "width": JJ['Frequency'] / 50,
}


plt.figure(figsize=(15, 10))
nx.draw_circular(G,  **options, with_labels = True)
ax = plt.gca()
plt.title('Flight Source-Target', fontsize=18)

plt.show()

DIC = {}

for i in list(zip(JJ['Source'], JJ['Target'])):
    if i not in DIC:
        DIC.setdefault(i, 1)
    else:
        DIC[i] += 1

In [189]:
G = nx.DiGraph()
for i in DIC:
    G.add_edge(i[0], i[1])
    G.edges[i]['weight'] = DIC[i]
    

options = {
    "font_size": 12,
    "node_size": 10,
    "node_color": "#A0CBE2",
    "edge_color": "skyblue",
    "linewidths": 1,
}

plt.figure(figsize=(10, 8))
nx.draw_circular(G,  **options, with_labels = True, width=[G[u][v]['weight']/60 for u, v in G.edges()])
ax = plt.gca()
plt.title('Flight Source-Target', fontsize=18)

plt.show()
